title: Unable to run training of the DLC model on GO
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

When running the training of a Deeplabcut model I ran into an unknown error

### Operating System

Google Colab

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu

### Steps To Reproduce

1. In Google Colab 
2. Run training of a model.
3. It should give the error

### Relevant log output

_No response_
